title: The Truckers Freedom Rally - astrology in action!
cleaned_text:
On Sunday, Jan 23, hundreds of truckers embarked for Ottawa from Vancouver in protest of the federal government’s new vaccine mandates for cross-border truckers. The convoy keeps growing in support, size and backing as the mandates and convoy affect food distribution.

The astrology set for 29th January when convoy is expected to arrive at the Canadian Capital(midday time) shows:

– conjunct Pluto, power of mass movement, being overpowered or empowered, both also in Capricorn – Mars has also now in Capricorn, mobility, drive, passion, anger against the system

– joined by dwarf planet Sedna, refusing to do what is expected

– Jupiter, truth, justice is the midpoint of Mars and Sun – Saturn is the midpoint of Jupiter and agent of chaos, Eris – Venus stations at the midpoint of Jupiter and Saturn

– Sun also squares Uranus and meets Saturn in freedom for the people Aquarius – All the while we live through the ongoing Saturn/ Uranus squares, where fighting for freedom from control is most significant!
